==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Noun===
'''elative case'''

#{{grammar}}: [[case]] used to indicate movement '''out of''' something; for example, ''out of the house''. Some languages that make use of the elative are [[Finnish]], [[Hungarian]], and [[Estonian]].

